(41, 'STEM Laboratory Equipment Supplier in Ghana', 'stem-laboratory-equipment-supplier-in-ghana', 'STEM Laboratory Equipment Supplier in Ghana ISO Certified Manufacturer', 'STEM Lab Equipment Ghana, STEM Lab Kits Ghana, High Educational Lab', 'Get STEM laboratory equipment & Kits supply from ISO-certified manufacturer, trusted supplier In Ghana, East Africa. Reliable delivery partner, bulk tender supply contact us', '<h2>STEM Lab Equipment Supplier in Ghana&nbsp; ISO Certified Manufacturer &amp; Trusted Tender Supply Africa</h2><div><br></div><div><font size=\"3\">As a trusted STEM lab equipment supplier in Ghana, we specialize in manufacturing and supplying high-quality scientific, educational, research, medical, and industrial laboratory equipment for universities, research institutions, testing laboratories, healthcare facilities, government projects, and private organizations across Ghana and Africa.</font></div><div><font size=\"3\">Our commitment to quality, innovation, and customer satisfaction has positioned us as a preferred partner for STEM laboratory infrastructure development and institutional procurement projects. Ghana\'s laboratory sector continues to demand reliable scientific equipment and turnkey laboratory solutions to support education, healthcare, mining, agriculture, and industrial research.</font></div><div><font size=\"3\"><br></font></div><h2><font size=\"3\">ISO Certified Laboratory Equipment Manufacturer</font></h2><div><font size=\"3\"><br></font></div><div><font size=\"3\">We manufacture and supply STEM laboratory equipment and STEM Lab Kits under stringent quality management systems, ensuring precision, durability, and compliance with international standards. Our product portfolio includes:</font></div><div><font size=\"3\"><br></font></div><div><font size=\"3\"><div>&nbsp;- Civil Engineering Laboratory Equipment Kits</div><div>&nbsp;- <a href=\"https://aticoscientific.com/category/physics-lab-equipment\" title=\"Physics Lab Equipment Kits\" target=\"\"><b>Physics Laboratory Equipment Kits</b></a></div><div>&nbsp;- Chemistry Laboratory Equipment Kits</div><div>&nbsp;- Biology Laboratory Equipment Kits</div><div>&nbsp;- Medical Laboratory Equipment Kits</div><div>&nbsp;- Environmental Testing Instruments Kits</div><div>&nbsp;- Agricultural Research Equipment Kits</div><div>&nbsp;- Industrial Testing Equipment Kits</div><div>&nbsp;- Laboratory Glassware &amp; Consumables Kits</div><div>&nbsp;- Laboratory Furniture &amp; Turnkey Lab Solutions Kits</div><div><br></div><h2>Trusted Tender Supply Partner Across Africa</h2><div><br></div><div>We are a reliable partner for government tenders, donor-funded projects, educational institutions, technical colleges, universities, NGOs, and laboratory modernization initiatives throughout Ghana and Africa. Our expertise covers complete project execution, including equipment supply, installation, commissioning, training, calibration, and after-sales support.</div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"https://aticolabexport.com/uploads/blog_images/934112STEM-KIt-Manufacturers.png\" alt=\"STEM Lab Equipment Supplier Ghana\" align=\"none\"></div><div><br></div><h3>Request a Quotation Today</h3><div><br></div><div>Looking for a reliable STEM Laboratory Equipment Supplier in Ghana, an ISO Certified Laboratory Equipment Manufacturer, or a Trusted Tender Supply Partner in Africa? Contact our team today for customized laboratory solutions, competitive tender pricing, and reliable project execution tailored to your institution\'s requirements.</div></font></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div>', '648961STEM-lab-equipment-Ghana.webp', 1, 2, NULL, NULL, '2026-06-23 11:57:18', '2026-06-23 11:57:18', NULL),
(42, 'Chemistry Lab Equipment Supplier in Ghana ISO Certified Manufacturer', 'chemistry-lab-equipment-supplier-in-ghana-iso-certified-manufacturer', 'Chemistry Lab Equipment Supplier in Ghana | ISO Certified Manufacturer', 'Chemistry Lab Equipment Ghana, Chemistry Lab Equipment Supplier', 'Atico Scientific, trusted chemistry lab equipment and lab kits supplier in Ghana. Manufacturing expertise and international export experienced, partner with us.', '<h2>Leading Chemistry Lab Equipment Supplier in Ghana ISO Manufacturing</h2><div><br></div><div><div><font size=\"3\">Atico Scientific, as a trusted <a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/category/chemistry-lab-equipment\" title=\"Chemistry Lab Equipment Supplier Ghana\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Chemistry Lab Equipment Supplier</b></a> in Ghana, we provide comprehensive laboratory solutions for educational institutions, universities, research centers, industrial laboratories, healthcare facilities, and government-funded projects. Our extensive range of chemistry laboratory equipment and lab kits is designed to support practical science education, chemical analysis, quality control, and advanced research applications.</font></div></div><div><font size=\"3\"><div>With years of manufacturing expertise and international export experience, we support institutions across Ghana and East Africa establish modern, fully equipped chemistry laboratories that meet global educational and research standards.</div><div><br></div><div><h2>ISO Certified Manufactured Chemistry Laboratory Equipment List&nbsp;</h2></div><div><div><br></div><div>As an ISO Certified Manufacturer, we maintain strict quality assurance processes throughout production. Our laboratory equipment is engineered for accuracy, durability, safety, and long-term performance.</div></div><div><br></div><div><div>&nbsp;- <a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/category/laboratory-glassware\" title=\"Chemistry Lab Equipment Manufacturer\" target=\"_blank\">Chemistry Laboratory Glassware</a></div><div>&nbsp;- <a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/product/balances\" title=\"Analytical Balance Manufacturer\" target=\"_blank\">Analytical &amp; Precision Balances</a></div><div>&nbsp;- <a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/product/hot-plate\" title=\"Hot Plate Manufacturer\" target=\"_blank\">Hot Plates and Magnetic Stirrers</a></div><div>&nbsp;- <a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/product/distillation-columns\" title=\"Lab Distilation Manufacturer\" target=\"_blank\">Laboratory Distillation Units</a></div><div>&nbsp;- <a href=\"https://ftirspectro.com/ftir-spectrophotometer.html\" title=\"FTIR Spectrophotometer Manufacturer\" target=\"_blank\">Spectrophotometers</a></div><div>&nbsp;- pH Meters and Conductivity Meters</div><div>&nbsp;- Fume Hoods and Chemical Storage Cabinets</div><div>&nbsp;- <a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/product/laboratory-oven\" title=\"Laboratory Oven Manufacturer\" target=\"_blank\">Laboratory Ovens and Furnaces</a></div><div>&nbsp;- <a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/product/water-purification-system\" title=\"Water Purification System Manufacturer\" target=\"_blank\">Water Purification Systems</a></div><div>&nbsp;- <a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/category/chemistry-lab-safety-equipments\" title=\"Laboratory Safety Equipment Manufacturer\" target=\"_blank\">Laboratory Safety Equipment</a></div><div>&nbsp;- Titration and Analytical Instruments</div></div><div><br></div><div><h2>Trusted Equipment Tender Supply Across East African Countries</h2></div><div><br></div><div><div>We are a reliable partner for laboratory equipment tenders and institutional procurement projects across: <b><i>Ghana Kenya Uganda Tanzania Rwanda Ethiopia Zambia Malawi South Sudan </i></b>Our dedicated tender support team manages complete project execution, including product sourcing, documentation, export logistics, installation, commissioning, training, and after-sales support.</div></div><div><img src=\"https://aticoscientific.com/uploads/blog_images/936132chemistry-lab-supplier-ghana.webp\" alt=\"Chemistry Lab Equipment Supplier In Ghana\" align=\"none\"></div><div><br></div><div><div>Looking for a dependable <a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/category/chemistry-lab-equipment\" title=\"Chemistry Lab Equipment\" target=\"_blank\">chemistry lab equipment supplier</a> in Ghana, Chemistry Lab Kit Supply Ghana, an ISO Certified Manufacturer, or a trusted Equipment Tender Supply Partner for East African Countries? Contact us today for customized laboratory solutions, competitive pricing, and expert support for your next laboratory project.</div></div></font></div><div><br></div>', '936132chemistry-lab-supplier-ghana.webp', 1, 2, 2, NULL, '2026-06-23 13:04:07', '2026-06-23 13:04:07', NULL);

